rrari demonstrates how sacrifice functioned in relation to other elements of fascist rhetoric, such as the frequent reiterations of an impending national crisis, the need for collaboration among social classes, and the forging of social contact between the leader and the people.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Aug 2021) 0aFascism and literaturezItaly. 0aRhetoricxPolitical aspectszItaly. 0aSacrifice in literature. 0aSacrificexPolitical aspectszItaly. 4aDISCOUNT-B. 7aHISTORY / Europe / Italy.2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.3138/978144266333640uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781442663336423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9781442663336.jpg  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_HICS  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_HICS  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK